#355"},{"id":91,"type":"VAELoader","pos":[17850,8090],"size":[500,60],"flags":{},"order":3,"mode":4,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"VAE","type":"VAE","links":[175]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.6.0","Node name for S&R":"VAELoader"},"widgets_values":["ae.safetensors"],"color":"#233","bgcolor":"#355"},{"id":124,"type":"CheckpointLoaderSimple","pos":[17850,7550],"size":[500,100],"flags":{},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"MODEL","type":"MODEL","links":[217]},{"name":"CLIP","type":"CLIP","links":[218]},{"name":"VAE","type":"VAE","links":[220]}],"title":"📦 Load Z-Anime Checkpoint","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.18.1","Node name for S&R":"CheckpointLoaderSimple"},"widgets_values":["z-anime-distill-8step-aio-fp8.safetensors"],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":127,"type":"VAELoader","pos":[17850,7370],"size":[500,60],"flags":{},"order":5,"mode":4,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"VAE","type":"VAE","links":[223]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.6.0","Node name for S&R":"VAELoader"},"widgets_values":["ae.safetensors"],"color":"#323","bgcolor":"#535"},{"id":126,"type":"CLIPLoaderGGUF","pos":[17850,7230],"size":[500,90],"flags":{},"order":6,"mode":4,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"CLIP","type":"CLIP","links":[224]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"ComfyUI-GGUF","ver":"6ea2651e7df66d7585f6ffee804b20e92fb38b8a","Node name for S&R":"CLIPLoaderGGUF"},"widgets_values":["qwen_3_4b-fp8.safetensors","qwen_image"],"color":"#323","bgcolor":"#535"},{"id":93,"type":"SaveImage","pos":[20180.122390790217,7050.2438982655885],"size":[470,780],"flags":{"pinned":true},"order":34,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"images","type":"IMAGE","link":170}],"outputs":[],"title":"💾 Save Z-Anime","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.18.0","Node name for S&R":"SaveImage"},"widgets_values":["Z-Anime"],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":95,"type":"SaveImage","pos":[21070,7100],"size":[540,1000],"flags":{"pinned":true},"order":42,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"images","type":"IMAGE","link":182}],"outputs":[],"title":"💾 Save Z-Anime Upscaled","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.18.0","Node name for S&R":"SaveImage"},"widgets_values":["Z-Anime-Upscale"],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":128,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[17180,7050],"size":[630,1120],"flags":{"pinned":true},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"🎌 Z-Anime Workflow Guide","properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.4.1","widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["## 🚀 Getting Started\n\nWelcome to the official Z-Anime ComfyUI Workflow!\nFollow the steps below from top to bottom and you'll have your first image in no time.\n\n---\n\n## 📦 Step 1 — Load Your Model\n\nThere are three loaders available depending on which version you downloaded.\nUse the **📦 Step 1 - Load Models Switch** node to select the right one by toggling **Yes / No**.\nOnly one loader should be active at a time.\n\n**📦 Load GGUF Models**\nFor all GGUF variants (Q4, Q8, etc.)\n\n**📦 Load Checkpoint Models**\nFor all AIO (All-in-One) versions — VAE and Text Encoder already included.\n\n**📦 Load Diffusion Models**\nFor all Diffusion format versions — loads UNet, CLIP and VAE separately.\n\n> Make sure the correct model file is selected inside the active loader node before generating.\n\n---\n\n## ✍️ Step 2 — Write Your Prompt\n\nWrite your prompt in the **✨ Positive Prompt** node.\n\n**Tip:** Look up a Z-Image prompting guide and feed it to an AI like ChatGPT — then ask it to write prompts for you. Z-Anime works best with natural, detailed descriptions rather than short tag lists.\n\nFor **Z-Anime Base** the negative prompt is fully supported and strongly recommended.\nFor the **Distill variants** (8-Step / 4-Step) the negative prompt has limited effect — you can leave it empty.\n\n---\n\n## 📐 Step 3 — Choose Your Resolution\n\nSet your output resolution in the **📐 Image Size** node.\n\nCheck the **📐 Resolution Guide** node for recommended presets:\n\n- **832 × 1216** — Portrait / Character art ⭐\n- **1216 × 832** — Landscape / Scenes\n- **1024 × 1024** — Square\n- **768 × 1344** — Full body / Tall\n- **1920 × 1088** — Cinematic / Widescreen\n- **1024 × 1536** — High quality portrait\n\n---\n\n## 🎨 Step 4 — Generate Your Image\n\nThis step contains two nodes:\n\n**🎲 Seed Control**\nSet your seed here. Switch to **fixed** if you want to reproduce the exact same image with the same prompt and settings. Switch to **randomize** to get a new result every run.\n\n**🎨 Generate Image**\nAdjust the settings depending on which model version you are using:\n\n*Z-Anime Base:*\n```\nSteps:  28–50\nCFG:    3.0–5.0\n```\n\n*Z-Anime Distill-8-Step:*\n```\nSteps:  8\nCFG:    1.0  (max ~1.5)\n```\n\n*Z-Anime Distill-4-Step:*\n```\nSteps:  4\nCFG:    1.0  (max ~1.5)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔼 Step 5 — Upscale (Optional)\n\nToggle the upscaler on or off with the **🔼 Toggle Upscaler ON/OFF** node.\n\n**📏 Scale Image**\nSets the upscale multiplier. Default is **1.5×**.\n\nExample:\nA 1024 × 1024 image at 1.5× becomes **1536 × 1536**.\n\n**🔄 Upscale Sampler**\nUses the same settings as **🎨 Generate Image** with one extra option — **Denoise**.\n\nThe Denoise value controls how much the upscaler changes your image:\n- **0.0** — no change, just larger\n- **0.35** — default, adds fine detail while keeping the original look ⭐\n- **1.0** — completely new image\n\n**🔍 Compare Images**\nUse this node to compare your original image side by side with the upscaled result.\n\n---\n\n*Happy generating!* 🎌"],"color":"#2d2d4d","bgcolor":"#3d3d70"},{"id":89,"type":"CLIPLoader","pos":[17850,7930],"size":[500,110],"flags":{},"order":8,"mode":4,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"CLIP","type":"CLIP","links":[174]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.6.0","Node name for S&R":"CLIPLoader"},"widgets_values":["qwen_3_4b-bf16.safetensors","qwen_image","cpu"],"color":"#233","bgcolor":"#355"},{"id":6,"type":"EmptyLatentImage","pos":[19270,7710],"size":[240,110],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":9,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"LATENT","type":"LATENT","links":[248]}],"title":"📐 Image Size","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.65","Node name for S&R":"EmptyLatentImage","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{"width":true,"height":true,"batch_size":true},"version":"7.0.1"}},"widgets_values":[1024,1536,1],"color":"#1a4d4d","bgcolor":"#2a7070"},{"id":28,"type":"Fast Groups Bypasser (rgthree)","pos":[20680,6940],"size":[360,60],"flags":{},"order":10,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"OPT_CONNECTION","type":"*","links":null}],"title":"🔼 Toggle Upscaler ON/OFF","properties":{"matchColors":"","matchTitle":"🔼","showNav":true,"showAllGraphs":true,"sort":"position","customSortAlphabet":"","toggleRestriction":"default","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4.1"}},"color":"#4d1a4d","bgcolor":"#702a70"},{"id":17,"type":"KSampler","pos":[19840,7100],"size":[300,710],"flags":{},"order":31,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"model","type":"MODEL","link":41},{"name":"positive","type":"CONDITIONING","link":229},{"name":"negative","type":"CONDITIONING","link":184},{"name":"latent_image","type":"LATENT","link":248},{"name":"seed","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"seed"},"link":69}],"outputs":[{"name":"LATENT","type":"LATENT","slot_index":0,"links":[8]}],"title":"🎨 Generate Image","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.48","Node name for S&R":"KSampler","ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}},"enableTabs":false,"tabWidth":65,"tabXOffset":10,"hasSecondTab":false,"secondTabText":"Send Back","secondTabOffset":80,"secondTabWidth":65},"widgets_values":[504463686355241,"fixed",10,1.1,"euler","beta",1],"color":"#3d1f5c","bgcolor":"#5c3080"},{"id":125,"type":"UnetLoaderGGUF","pos":[17850,7110],"size":[500,60],"flags":{},"order":11,"mode":4,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"MODEL","type":"MODEL","links":[225]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"ComfyUI-GGUF","ver":"6ea2651e7df66d7585f6ffee804b20e92fb38b8a","Node name for S&R":"UnetLoaderGGUF"},"widgets_values":["z-anime-base-q8_0.gguf"],"color":"#323","bgcolor":"#535"},{"id":23,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[16550,7050],"size":[610,1120],"flags":{"pinned":true},"order":12,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"📖 Z-Anime Info","properties":{"ue_properties":{"version":"7.4.1","widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["# 🎌 Z-Anime\n\n**Full Fine-Tune on Z-Image (Base)** — Anime-optimized model with rich aesthetics, strong diversity and full negative prompt support.\n\n---\n\n## ⚡ Quick Start\n\n1. Load model (BF16, FP8, GGUF or AIO)\n2. Write your prompt\n3. Set resolution\n4. Generate!\n\n---\n\n## ⚙️ Settings by Variant\n\n### 🎌 Z-Anime Base\n```yaml\nsteps: 28–50\ncfg: 3.0–5.0  (up to 9.0 possible)\nsampler: euler_ancestral ⭐\nscheduler: beta ⭐\nnegative: strongly recommended\n```\n\n### ⚡ Z-Anime-Distill-8-Step\n```yaml\nsteps: 8\ncfg: 1.0  (max ~1.5)\nsampler: euler_ancestral\nscheduler: beta\nnegative: limited effect\n```\n\n### 🚀 Z-Anime-Distill-4-Step\n```yaml\nsteps: 4\ncfg: 1.0  (max ~1.5)\nsampler: euler_ancestral\nscheduler: beta\nnegative: limited effect\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📦 Versions\n\n| Version | Prec. | Size | Use Case |\n|---------|-------|------|----------|\n| 🎌 Z-Anime Base | BF16 | ~12GB | Max quality |\n| 🎌 Z-Anime Base | FP8 | ~6GB | Daily use |\n| ⚡ Z-Anime-Distill-8-Step | BF16 | ~12GB | Fast + quality |\n| ⚡ Z-Anime-Distill-8-Step | FP8 | ~6GB | Fast, low VRAM |\n| 🚀 Z-Anime-Distill-4-Step | BF16 | ~12GB | Ultra fast |\n| 🚀 Z-Anime-Distill-4-Step | FP8 | ~6GB | Ultra fast, low VRAM |\n| 📦 GGUF Q8_0 | — | ~6.7GB | Low VRAM / CPU |\n| 📦 GGUF Q4_K_S | — | ~4.2GB | Very low VRAM |\n| 📦 AIO Base + 4-Step + 8-Step | BF16/FP8 | varies | Single-file (VAE+TE built-in) |\n\nAll versions run on **8GB VRAM**!\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Features\n\n✅ Rich anime style & aesthetics\n✅ Strong diversity (identities, poses, layouts)\n✅ Full negative prompt support (Base)\n✅ Natural language prompts\n✅ Fine-tunable — LoRA training ready\n✅ High resolution (up to 2048×2048)\n✅ Partially NSFW capable\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Desktop ComfyUI Issue\n\nIf metadata save fails, replace **\"💾 Save Z-Anime\"** nodes with standard **\"Save Image\"** node.\n\n---\n\n## 📥 Links\n\n- [CivitAI Page](https://civitai.red/models/2483351)\n- [HuggingFace Repo](https://huggingface.co/SeeSee21/Z-Anime)\n- [Author — SeeSee21](https://huggingface.co/SeeSee21)\n\n---\n\n## 📦 Custom Nodes\n\n- [rgthree-comfy](https://github.com/rgthree/rgthree-comfy)\n- [ComfyUI-Lora-Manager](https://github.com/willmiao/ComfyUI-Lora-Manager)\n- [ComfyUI-GGUF](https://github.com/city96/ComfyUI-GGUF) *(for GGUF loaders)*\n- [ComfyUI-SeedVR2_VideoUpscaler](https://github.com/numz/ComfyUI-SeedVR2_VideoUpscaler) *(optional)*"],"color":"#2d2d4d","bgcolor":"#3d3d70"},{"id":60,"type":"Reroute","pos":[20570,6970],"size":[75,26],"flags":{},"order":20,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"","type":"*","link":83}],"outputs":[{"name":"","type":"VAE","links":[84,249]}],"properties":{"showOutputText":false,"horizontal":false},"color":"#4d2d1a","bgcolor":"#704a2a"},{"id":20,"type":"CLIPTextEncode","pos":[19000,7100],"size":[510,490],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":22,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":161}],"outputs":[{"name":"CONDITIONING","type":"CONDITIONING","links":[227]}],"title":"✨ Positive Prompt","properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.65","Node name for S&R":"CLIPTextEncode","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{"text":true},"version":"7.0.1"}},"widgets_values":["A young anime girl with long flowing silver hair and bright expressive blue eyes, wearing a detailed school uniform with a navy blazer and red ribbon. She stands by an open classroom window in late afternoon, soft sunlight filtering through, cherry blossom petals drifting in the warm breeze. Gentle rim light on her hair, detailed fabric folds, expressive calm face, clean line work, professional anime illustration with rich color, fine detail and a soft cinematic atmosphere."],"color":"#1e3a2f","bgcolor":"#2d5a47"},{"id":88,"type":"Lora Loader (LoraManager)","pos":[18410,7220],"size":[530,930],"flags":{},"order":19,"mode":4,"inputs":[{"name":"model","type":"MODEL","link":179},{"name":"clip","shape":7,"type":"CLIP","link":180},{"name":"lora_stack","shape":7,"type":"LORA_STACK","link":null}],"outputs":[{"name":"MODEL","type":"MODEL","links":[162]},{"name":"CLIP","type":"CLIP","links":[161,183]},{"name":"trigger_words","type":"STRING","links":null},{"name":"loaded_loras","type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-lora-manager","ver":"0.9.11","Node name for S&R":"Lora Loader (LoraManager)","__lm_widget_ids":["__lm_autocomplete_meta_text","text","loras"]},"widgets_values":[{"version":1,"textWidgetName":"text"},"",[]],"color":"#2a363b","bgcolor":"#3f5159"},{"id":43,"type":"Fast Groups Bypasser (rgthree)","pos":[18390,7050],"size":[570,60],"flags":{},"order":13,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"OPT_CONNECTION","type":"*","links":null}],"title":"📖 Toggle LoRA  ON/OFF","properties":{"matchColors":"","matchTitle":"📖","showNav":true,"showAllGraphs":true,"sort":"position","customSortAlphabet":"","toggleRestriction":"default","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4.1"}},"color":"#4d1a4d","bgcolor":"#702a70"},{"id":92,"type":"Fast Groups Bypasser (rgthree)","pos":[17820,6880],"size":[400,110],"flags":{},"order":14,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"OPT_CONNECTION","type":"*","links":null}],"title":"📦 Step 1 - Load Models Switch","properties":{"matchColors":"","matchTitle":"📦","showNav":true,"showAllGraphs":true,"sort":"position","customSortAlphabet":"","toggleRestriction":"max one","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.4.1"}},"color":"#4d1a4d","bgcolor":"#702a70"}],"links":[[8,17,0,11,0,"LATENT"],[10,14,0,12,0,"LAT